## 3. Matrix – Tier 1: Dedicated Entities

Dedicated entities have their own DB tables and detail views.

Legend: **Y** = yes, show/support | **—** = no, hide/skip | **Σ** = show summary/aggregate only (no direct items)

| Panel / Table | DataDomain | DataProduct | DataContract | CompliancePolicy | Concept | Collection |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Costs** | Σ | Y | Y | — | — | — |
| **Quality** | Σ | Y | Y | — | — | — |
| **Comments** | Y | Y | Y | Y | — | — |
| **Ratings** | — | Y | Y | — | — | — |
| **Relationships** | Y | Y | Y | — | — | — |
| **Subscriptions** | — | Y | Y | — | — | — |
| **Tags** | — | Y | Y | — | — | — |
| **Semantic Links** | — | — | Y | — | — | — |
| **Metadata (rich/link/doc)** | Y | Y | Y | Y | Y | Y |
| **Change Log** | — | Y | Y | — | — | — |
| **Access Grants** | — | Y | — | — | — | — |
| **Agreements / Approvals** | — | Y | Y | — | — | — |
| **Ownership** | Y | Y | Y | — | Y | — |
| **Lineage** | — | Y | Y | — | — | — |
| **Impact Analysis** | — | — | — | Y | — | — |
| **Hierarchy** | — | Y | — | — | — | — |
| **Version History** | — | — | Y | — | — | — |

### Notes – Tier 1

- **DataDomain costs:** domains don't carry direct cost items. The UI may show a
  **summary** (Σ) aggregated from child products/contracts, but should never offer
  "Add cost item" on a domain.
- **DataDomain quality:** same as costs – aggregate-only from child products.
- **DataProduct quality:** uses `productAggregation` prop to auto-roll-up scores
  from child contracts. Also accepts direct product-level measurements.
- **Team, Project, BusinessRole, ProcessWorkflow, GenieSpace, SemanticModel, MdmConfig,
  AssetReview** currently have **no** polymorphic panel integration. If panels are
  added later, update this matrix.

